{
  "video_id": "5qaktKVL_zM",
  "title": "What we can do to die well | Timothy Ihrig",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13387.0,
      "end_time": 14936.0,
      "text": "I am a palliative care physician"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14936.0,
      "end_time": 18393.0,
      "text": "and I would like to talk to you today about health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18393.0,
      "end_time": 22917.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to talk to you about the health and care"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22917.0,
      "end_time": 25788.0,
      "text": "of the most vulnerable population in our country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25788.0,
      "end_time": 32202.0,
      "text": "those people dealing with the most complex serious health issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32202.0,
      "end_time": 35028.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to talk to you about economics as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35028.0,
      "end_time": 39508.0,
      "text": "And the intersection of these two should scare the hell out of you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39508.0,
      "end_time": 42199.0,
      "text": "it scares the hell out of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42199.0,
      "end_time": 45835.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d also like to talk to you about palliative medicine:"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45835.0,
      "end_time": 52544.0,
      "text": "a paradigm of care for this population, grounded in what they value."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52544.0,
      "end_time": 55765.0,
      "text": "Patient-centric care based on their values"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 55765.0,
      "end_time": 60458.0,
      "text": "that helps this population live better and longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60458.0,
      "end_time": 63744.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a care model that tells the truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63744.0,
      "end_time": 65008.0,
      "text": "and engages one-on-one"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 65007.99999999999,
      "end_time": 69460.0,
      "text": "and meets people where they&#39;re at."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 69460.0,
      "end_time": 73247.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to start by telling the story of my very first patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73247.0,
      "end_time": 75307.0,
      "text": "It was my first day as a physician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75307.0,
      "end_time": 77519.0,
      "text": "with the long white coat ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77519.0,
      "end_time": 79025.0,
      "text": "I stumbled into the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79025.0,
      "end_time": 81849.0,
      "text": "and right away there&#39;s a gentleman, Harold, 68 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81849.0,
      "end_time": 83474.0,
      "text": "came to the emergency department."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83474.0,
      "end_time": 85481.0,
      "text": "He had had headaches for about six weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85481.0,
      "end_time": 88460.0,
      "text": "that got worse and worse and worse and worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88460.0,
      "end_time": 93148.0,
      "text": "Evaluation revealed he had cancer that had spread to his brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93148.0,
      "end_time": 99791.0,
      "text": "The attending physician directed me to go share with Harold and his family"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99791.0,
      "end_time": 104114.0,
      "text": "the diagnosis, the prognosis and options of care."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104114.0,
      "end_time": 107092.0,
      "text": "Five hours into my new career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107092.0,
      "end_time": 109922.0,
      "text": "I did the only thing I knew how."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109922.0,
      "end_time": 111790.0,
      "text": "I walked in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111790.0,
      "end_time": 113717.0,
      "text": "sat down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113717.0,
      "end_time": 115935.0,
      "text": "took Harold&#39;s hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115935.0,
      "end_time": 118142.0,
      "text": "took his wife&#39;s hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118142.0,
      "end_time": 120500.0,
      "text": "and just breathed."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120500.0,
      "end_time": 123132.0,
      "text": "He said, &quot;It&#39;s not good news is it, sonny?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123132.0,
      "end_time": 124564.0,
      "text": "I said, &quot;No.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124564.0,
      "end_time": 128867.0,
      "text": "And so we talked and we listened and we shared."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 128866.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130123.99999999999,
      "text": "And after a while I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130124.0,
      "end_time": 133373.0,
      "text": "&quot;Harold, what is it that has meaning to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133373.0,
      "end_time": 135026.0,
      "text": "What is it that you hold sacred?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135026.0,
      "end_time": 136365.0,
      "text": "And he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136365.0,
      "end_time": 138525.0,
      "text": "&quot;My family.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138525.0,
      "end_time": 140570.0,
      "text": "I said, &quot;What do you want to do?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140570.0,
      "end_time": 143761.0,
      "text": "He slapped me on the knee and said, &quot;I want to go fishing.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143761.0,
      "end_time": 146646.0,
      "text": "I said, &quot;That, I know how to do.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146646.0,
      "end_time": 149760.0,
      "text": "Harold went fishing the next day."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149760.0,
      "end_time": 152455.0,
      "text": "He died a week later."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152455.0,
      "end_time": 155098.0,
      "text": "As I&#39;ve gone through my training in my career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155098.0,
      "end_time": 156609.0,
      "text": "I think back to Harold."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156609.0,
      "end_time": 160782.0,
      "text": "And I think that this is a conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160782.0,
      "end_time": 163737.0,
      "text": "that happens far too infrequently."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163737.0,
      "end_time": 168173.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a conversation that had led us to crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168173.0,
      "end_time": 170861.0,
      "text": "to the biggest threat to the American way of life today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170861.0,
      "end_time": 173926.0,
      "text": "which is health care expenditures."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173926.0,
      "end_time": 175127.0,
      "text": "So what do we know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175127.0,
      "end_time": 178080.0,
      "text": "We know that this population, the most ill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178080.0,
      "end_time": 180688.0,
      "text": "takes up 15 percent of the gross domestic product --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180688.0,
      "end_time": 184307.0,
      "text": "nearly 2.3 trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184307.0,
      "end_time": 187891.0,
      "text": "So the sickest 15 percent take up 15 percent of the GDP."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 187891.0,
      "end_time": 191755.0,
      "text": "If we extrapolate this out over the next two decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 191755.0,
      "end_time": 194838.0,
      "text": "with the growth of baby boomers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194838.0,
      "end_time": 200177.0,
      "text": "at this rate it is 60 percent of the GDP."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200177.0,
      "end_time": 202480.0,
      "text": "Sixty percent of the gross domestic product"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202480.0,
      "end_time": 204128.0,
      "text": "of the United States of America --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204128.0,
      "end_time": 207148.0,
      "text": "it has very little to do with health care at that point."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207148.0,
      "end_time": 209540.0,
      "text": "It has to do with a gallon of milk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209540.0,
      "end_time": 211625.0,
      "text": "with college tuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211625.0,
      "end_time": 214112.0,
      "text": "It has to do with every thing that we value"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214112.0,
      "end_time": 218514.0,
      "text": "and every thing that we know presently."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218514.0,
      "end_time": 222729.0,
      "text": "It has at stake the free-market economy and capitalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222729.0,
      "end_time": 226965.0,
      "text": "of the United States of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 226965.0,
      "end_time": 230145.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s forget all the statistics for a minute, forget the numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230145.0,
      "end_time": 234822.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about the value we get for all these dollars we spend."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 234822.0,
      "end_time": 237439.0,
      "text": "Well, the Dartmouth Atlas, about six years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237439.0,
      "end_time": 240216.0,
      "text": "looked at every dollar spent by Medicare --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 240216.0,
      "end_time": 241851.0,
      "text": "generally this population."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241851.0,
      "end_time": 248050.0,
      "text": "We found that those patients who have the highest per capita expenditures"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248050.0,
      "end_time": 252182.0,
      "text": "had the highest suffering, pain, depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252182.0,
      "end_time": 255824.0,
      "text": "And, more often than not, they die sooner."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255824.0,
      "end_time": 257789.0,
      "text": "How can this be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257789.0,
      "end_time": 259217.0,
      "text": "We live in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259216.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261730.99999999997,
      "text": "it has the greatest health care system on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261731.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "We spend 10 times more on these patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267196.0,
      "text": "than the second-leading country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 267196.0,
      "end_time": 269764.0,
      "text": "That doesn&#39;t make sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269764.0,
      "end_time": 271147.0,
      "text": "But what we know is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271147.0,
      "end_time": 274342.0,
      "text": "out of the top 50 countries on the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 274342.0,
      "end_time": 277949.0,
      "text": "with organized health care systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277949.0,
      "end_time": 282017.0,
      "text": "we rank 37th."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282017.0,
      "end_time": 286327.0,
      "text": "Former Eastern Bloc countries and sub-Saharan African countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286327.0,
      "end_time": 292485.0,
      "text": "rank higher than us as far as quality and value."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 292485.0,
      "end_time": 295047.0,
      "text": "Something I experience every day in my practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 295047.0,
      "end_time": 299927.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m sure, something many of you on your own journeys have experienced:"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299927.0,
      "end_time": 304196.0,
      "text": "more is not more."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304196.0,
      "end_time": 306209.0,
      "text": "Those individuals who had more tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306209.0,
      "end_time": 307503.0,
      "text": "more bells, more whistles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307503.0,
      "end_time": 309955.0,
      "text": "more chemotherapy, more surgery, more whatever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309955.0,
      "end_time": 313283.0,
      "text": "the more that we do to someone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313283.0,
      "end_time": 317422.0,
      "text": "it decreases the quality of their life."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317422.0,
      "end_time": 321896.0,
      "text": "And it shortens it, most often."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 321896.0,
      "end_time": 323745.0,
      "text": "So what are we going to do about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 323745.0,
      "end_time": 325461.0,
      "text": "What are we doing about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325461.0,
      "end_time": 327097.0,
      "text": "And why is this so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327097.0,
      "end_time": 329025.0,
      "text": "The grim reality, ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 329025.0,
      "end_time": 332447.0,
      "text": "is that we, the health care industry -- long white-coat physicians --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 332447.0,
      "end_time": 334877.0,
      "text": "are stealing from you."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 334877.0,
      "end_time": 337974.0,
      "text": "Stealing from you the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 337974.0,
      "end_time": 340358.0,
      "text": "to choose how you want to live your lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 340358.0,
      "end_time": 342863.0,
      "text": "in the context of whatever disease it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 342863.0,
      "end_time": 345656.0,
      "text": "We focus on disease and pathology and surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 345656.0,
      "end_time": 349319.0,
      "text": "and pharmacology."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349319.0,
      "end_time": 353434.0,
      "text": "We miss the human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 353434.0,
      "end_time": 354985.0,
      "text": "How can we treat this"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354985.0,
      "end_time": 359029.0,
      "text": "without understanding this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 359029.0,
      "end_time": 362948.0,
      "text": "We do things to this;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 362948.0,
      "end_time": 368161.0,
      "text": "we need to do things for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 368161.0,
      "end_time": 369965.0,
      "text": "The triple aim of healthcare:"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 369965.0,
      "end_time": 373081.0,
      "text": "one, improve patient experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373081.0,
      "end_time": 377467.0,
      "text": "Two, improve the population health."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 377467.0,
      "end_time": 383591.0,
      "text": "Three, decrease per capita expenditure across a continuum."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 383591.0,
      "end_time": 385358.0,
      "text": "Our group, palliative care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385358.0,
      "end_time": 391000.0,
      "text": "in 2012, working with the sickest of the sick --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 391000.0,
      "end_time": 392175.0,
      "text": "cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 392175.0,
      "end_time": 394017.0,
      "text": "heart disease, lung disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394017.0,
      "end_time": 395192.0,
      "text": "renal disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 395192.0,
      "end_time": 397681.0,
      "text": "dementia --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 397681.0,
      "end_time": 401010.0,
      "text": "how did we improve patient experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 401010.0,
      "end_time": 402633.0,
      "text": "&quot;I want to be at home, Doc.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402633.0,
      "end_time": 404868.0,
      "text": "&quot;OK, we&#39;ll bring the care to you.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404868.0,
      "end_time": 407732.0,
      "text": "Quality of life, enhanced."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 407732.0,
      "end_time": 409114.0,
      "text": "Think about the human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409114.0,
      "end_time": 411069.0,
      "text": "Two: population health."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 411069.0,
      "end_time": 413944.0,
      "text": "How did we look at this population differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 413944.0,
      "end_time": 416816.0,
      "text": "and engage with them at a different level, a deeper level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 416816.0,
      "end_time": 421091.0,
      "text": "and connect to a broader sense of the human condition than my own?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 421091.0,
      "end_time": 424584.0,
      "text": "How do we manage this group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 424584.0,
      "end_time": 426377.0,
      "text": "so that of our outpatient population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 426377.0,
      "end_time": 431919.0,
      "text": "94 percent, in 2012, never had to go to the hospital?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 431919.0,
      "end_time": 435213.0,
      "text": "Not because they couldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 435213.0,
      "end_time": 437022.0,
      "text": "But they didn&#39;t have to."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 437022.0,
      "end_time": 439356.0,
      "text": "We brought the care to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439356.0,
      "end_time": 445220.0,
      "text": "We maintained their value, their quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 445220.0,
      "end_time": 448746.0,
      "text": "Number three: per capita expenditures."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448746.0,
      "end_time": 450168.0,
      "text": "For this population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450168.0,
      "end_time": 455245.0,
      "text": "that today is 2.3 trillion dollars and in 20 years is 60 percent of the GDP,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 455245.0,
      "end_time": 460873.0,
      "text": "we reduced health care expenditures by nearly 70 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 460873.0,
      "end_time": 464346.0,
      "text": "They got more of what they wanted based on their values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464346.0,
      "end_time": 467464.0,
      "text": "lived better and are living longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 467464.0,
      "end_time": 474880.0,
      "text": "for two-thirds less money."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474880.0,
      "end_time": 477663.0,
      "text": "While Harold&#39;s time was limited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 477663.0,
      "end_time": 480288.0,
      "text": "palliative care&#39;s is not."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 480288.0,
      "end_time": 486677.0,
      "text": "Palliative care is a paradigm from diagnosis through the end of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 486677.0,
      "end_time": 488361.0,
      "text": "The hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 488361.0,
      "end_time": 491916.0,
      "text": "weeks, months, years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 491916.0,
      "end_time": 493098.0,
      "text": "across a continuum --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 493098.0,
      "end_time": 495006.0,
      "text": "with treatment, without treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 495006.0,
      "end_time": 497196.0,
      "text": "Meet Christine."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 497196.0,
      "end_time": 499151.0,
      "text": "Stage III cervical cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 499151.0,
      "end_time": 502196.0,
      "text": "so, metastatic cancer that started in her cervix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502196.0,
      "end_time": 504719.0,
      "text": "spread throughout her body."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 504719.0,
      "end_time": 508743.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s in her 50s and she is living."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 508743.0,
      "end_time": 510360.0,
      "text": "This is not about end of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 510360.0,
      "end_time": 513180.0,
      "text": "this is about life."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 513179.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515093.99999999994,
      "text": "This is not just about the elderly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 515094.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517929.00000000006,
      "text": "this is about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 517929.0,
      "end_time": 519706.0,
      "text": "This is Richard."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519706.0,
      "end_time": 522427.0,
      "text": "End-stage lung disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 522427.0,
      "end_time": 525581.0,
      "text": "&quot;Richard, what is it that you hold sacred?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 525581.0,
      "end_time": 529094.0,
      "text": "&quot;My kids, my wife and my Harley.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 529094.0,
      "end_time": 530129.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530129.0,
      "end_time": 532544.0,
      "text": "&quot;Alright!"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 532544.0,
      "end_time": 535806.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t drive you around on it because I can barely pedal a bicycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 535806.0,
      "end_time": 538385.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s see what we can do.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 538385.0,
      "end_time": 540946.0,
      "text": "Richard came to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 540946.0,
      "end_time": 544444.0,
      "text": "and he was in rough shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 544444.0,
      "end_time": 546249.0,
      "text": "He had this little voice telling him"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 546249.0,
      "end_time": 549488.0,
      "text": "that maybe his time was weeks to months."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 549488.0,
      "end_time": 550778.0,
      "text": "And then we just talked."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 550778.0,
      "end_time": 554891.0,
      "text": "And I listened and tried to hear --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 554891.0,
      "end_time": 556202.0,
      "text": "big difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 556202.0,
      "end_time": 560479.0,
      "text": "Use these in proportion to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 560479.0,
      "end_time": 563028.0,
      "text": "I said, &quot;Alright, let&#39;s take it one day at a time,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 563028.0,
      "end_time": 566573.0,
      "text": "like we do in every other chapter of our life."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 566573.0,
      "end_time": 571006.0,
      "text": "And we have met Richard where Richard&#39;s at day-to-day."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 571006.0,
      "end_time": 575059.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a phone call or two a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 575059.0,
      "end_time": 583040.0,
      "text": "but he&#39;s thriving in the context of end-stage lung disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 583040.0,
      "end_time": 585557.0,
      "text": "Now, palliative medicine is not just for the elderly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 585557.0,
      "end_time": 589535.0,
      "text": "it is not just for the middle-aged."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 589535.0,
      "end_time": 591090.0,
      "text": "It is for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 591090.0,
      "end_time": 593903.0,
      "text": "Meet my friend Jonathan."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 593903.0,
      "end_time": 595407.0,
      "text": "We have the honor and pleasure"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 595407.0,
      "end_time": 597751.0,
      "text": "of Jonathan and his father joining us here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 597751.0,
      "end_time": 600607.0,
      "text": "Jonathan is in his 20s, and I met him several years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 600607.0,
      "end_time": 604700.0,
      "text": "He was dealing with metastatic testicular cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 604700.0,
      "end_time": 606465.0,
      "text": "spread to his brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 606465.0,
      "end_time": 608375.0,
      "text": "He had a stroke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 608375.0,
      "end_time": 609947.0,
      "text": "he had brain surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 609947.0,
      "end_time": 613579.0,
      "text": "radiation, chemotherapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 613579.0,
      "end_time": 615399.0,
      "text": "Upon meeting him and his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 615399.0,
      "end_time": 618254.0,
      "text": "he was a couple of weeks away from a bone marrow transplant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 618254.0,
      "end_time": 620539.0,
      "text": "and in listening and engaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 620539.0,
      "end_time": 627764.0,
      "text": "they said, &quot;Help us understand -- what is cancer?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 627764.0,
      "end_time": 630513.0,
      "text": "How did we get this far"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 630513.0,
      "end_time": 633276.0,
      "text": "without understanding what we&#39;re dealing with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 633276.0,
      "end_time": 635714.0,
      "text": "How did we get this far without empowering somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 635714.0,
      "end_time": 637650.0,
      "text": "to know what it is they&#39;re dealing with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 637650.0,
      "end_time": 641282.0,
      "text": "and then taking the next step and engaging in who they are as human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 641282.0,
      "end_time": 643402.0,
      "text": "to know if that is what we should do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 643402.0,
      "end_time": 649133.0,
      "text": "Lord knows we can do any kind of thing to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 649133.0,
      "end_time": 653870.0,
      "text": "But should we?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 653870.0,
      "end_time": 655578.0,
      "text": "And don&#39;t take my word for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 655578.0,
      "end_time": 660054.0,
      "text": "All the evidence that is related to palliative care these days"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 660054.0,
      "end_time": 664199.0,
      "text": "demonstrates with absolute certainty people live better and live longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 664199.0,
      "end_time": 667567.0,
      "text": "There was a seminal article out of the New England Journal of Medicine"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 667567.0,
      "end_time": 669621.0,
      "text": "in 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 669621.0,
      "end_time": 672309.0,
      "text": "A study done at Harvard by friends of mine, colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 672309.0,
      "end_time": 673714.0,
      "text": "End-stage lung cancer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 673714.0,
      "end_time": 676695.0,
      "text": "one group with palliative care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 676695.0,
      "end_time": 679782.0,
      "text": "a similar group without."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 679782.0,
      "end_time": 683901.0,
      "text": "The group with palliative care reported less pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 683901.0,
      "end_time": 685556.0,
      "text": "less depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 685556.0,
      "end_time": 688487.0,
      "text": "They needed fewer hospitalizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 688487.0,
      "end_time": 690639.0,
      "text": "And, ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 690639.0,
      "end_time": 695805.0,
      "text": "they lived three to six months longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 695805.0,
      "end_time": 699867.0,
      "text": "If palliative care were a cancer drug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 699867.0,
      "end_time": 704845.0,
      "text": "every cancer doctor on the planet would write a prescription for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 704845.0,
      "end_time": 707570.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 707570.0,
      "end_time": 710938.0,
      "text": "Again, because we goofy, long white-coat physicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 710938.0,
      "end_time": 716401.0,
      "text": "are trained and of the mantra of dealing with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 716401.0,
      "end_time": 722697.0,
      "text": "not with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 722697.0,
      "end_time": 727709.0,
      "text": "This is a space that we will all come to at some point."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 727709.0,
      "end_time": 730457.0,
      "text": "But this conversation today is not about dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 730457.0,
      "end_time": 732289.0,
      "text": "it is about living."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 732289.0,
      "end_time": 733637.0,
      "text": "Living based on our values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 733637.0,
      "end_time": 735080.0,
      "text": "what we find sacred"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 735080.0,
      "end_time": 737521.0,
      "text": "and how we want to write the chapters of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 737521.0,
      "end_time": 739379.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s the last"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 739379.0,
      "end_time": 742258.0,
      "text": "or the last five."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 742258.0,
      "end_time": 744277.0,
      "text": "What we know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 744277.0,
      "end_time": 746475.0,
      "text": "what we have proven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 746475.0,
      "end_time": 749946.0,
      "text": "is that this conversation needs to happen today --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 749946.0,
      "end_time": 752029.0,
      "text": "not next week, not next year."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 752029.0,
      "end_time": 754883.0,
      "text": "What is at stake is our lives today"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 754883.0,
      "end_time": 756707.0,
      "text": "and the lives of us as we get older"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 756707.0,
      "end_time": 760310.0,
      "text": "and the lives of our children and our grandchildren."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 760310.0,
      "end_time": 762207.0,
      "text": "Not just in that hospital room"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 762207.0,
      "end_time": 764141.0,
      "text": "or on the couch at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 764141.0,
      "end_time": 768326.0,
      "text": "but everywhere we go and everything we see."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 768326.0,
      "end_time": 773570.0,
      "text": "Palliative medicine is the answer to engage with human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 773570.0,
      "end_time": 778304.0,
      "text": "to change the journey that we will all face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 778304.0,
      "end_time": 782148.0,
      "text": "and change it for the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 782148.0,
      "end_time": 784823.0,
      "text": "To my colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 784823.0,
      "end_time": 786702.0,
      "text": "to my patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 786702.0,
      "end_time": 788303.0,
      "text": "to my government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 788303.0,
      "end_time": 790386.0,
      "text": "to all human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 790386.0,
      "end_time": 794641.0,
      "text": "I ask that we stand and we shout and we demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 794641.0,
      "end_time": 797352.0,
      "text": "the best care possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 797352.0,
      "end_time": 799606.0,
      "text": "so that we can live better today"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 799606.0,
      "end_time": 801311.0,
      "text": "and ensure a better life tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 801311.0,
      "end_time": 804452.0,
      "text": "We need to shift today"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 804452.0,
      "end_time": 808838.0,
      "text": "so that we can live tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 808838.0,
      "end_time": 810013.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 810013.0,
      "end_time": 820013.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}